[[File:Galaxies_Opera_House_Posters.jpg|thumb|300px|Signs for ''Wicked'' and other shows outside the Galaxies Opera House]]
'''''Wicked''''' was a musical playing at the [[Galaxies Opera House/Legends|Galaxies Opera House]] in [[19 BBY/Legends|19 BBY]]. A sign advertising the show was displayed outside of the [[Opera/Legends|opera]] house during a performance of [[Squid Lake/Legends|''Squid Lake'']] attended by [[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine]] and [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Anakin Skywalker]]. The sign depicted an [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[Stormtrooper/Legends|stormtrooper]] whispering into the [[Ear/Legends|ear]] of a [[Color/Legends|green]]-skinned [[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine]].<ref name="Revenge of the Clone Menace">''[[Tag & Bink: Revenge of the Clone Menace]]''</ref>

==Behind the scenes==
This is a reference to the musical [[Wikipedia:Wicked (musical)|''Wicked'']]. In ''[[Tag & Bink: Revenge of the Clone Menace]]'', there is a poster resembling ''Wicked''{{'s}}, but instead of the show's characters Elphaba and Glinda, it shows a green [[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine]] and a [[Stormtrooper/Legends|stormtrooper]].

